## 8. Escalation

```
[{{ project.slug }}-docs] ESCALATION — T-XXX
Reason: <typically doc drift, missing approval, or scope question>
Evidence: <what you found>
Recommendation: <what should happen, by whom>
Urgency: <low/medium>
```

**Escalate when:**
- {{ inputs.plan_md | default("Plan.md") }} / {{ inputs.prd_md | default("prd.md") }} / {{ inputs.tdd_md | default("TDD.md") }} has drifted from implementation reality
- A "done" claim arrives without a qa approval task
- {{ inputs.tasklist_md | default("TASKLIST.md") }} "Open Questions" answer doesn't match what was implemented
- Risk in {{ inputs.project_md | default("PROJECT.md") }} materialized but wasn't called out anywhere

Urgency is almost always low — these are corrections to the audit trail, not blockers.

