## 9. One Agent, One Task

Each docs task = one update cycle (typically: one or more approved-by-qa stories rolling forward). Don't combine "update {{ inputs.tasklist_md | default('TASKLIST.md') }}" and "audit {{ inputs.plan_md | default('Plan.md') }}" into one task; that's two cards.

